title: Grateful Dead Live at Bakersfield Memorial Auditorium on 1978-01-14
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, Dire Wolf, Cassidy, They Love Each Other, Mama Tried-> Me & My Uncle, Loser, Looks Like Rain, Deal, Let It Grow

Set 2

Samson & Delilah, Candyman, Estimated Prophet-> Eyes Of The World-> Not Fade Away-> One More Saturday Night

reviews.review_text:
Thanks! I'm glad I didn't go to the basketball game...
Great MOTB efforts...
These small shows during this time period just rock. Listen to this one
- Not even close to the shows from earlier in the month, but OK.

Loser I had to make sure I wasn’t tripping in the middle of Loser. Snapped my fingers a few times and it sounded crisp, so it was definitely the recording. There’s a lag that causes the drums to blend high in the mix and the music slows down, like they were having trouble fighting through it on stage. Totally weird, but it took me into a strange reality questioning things around me.
